{"tid":369203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牛頭角13歲女童梁婷婷失蹤","createTime":"2017-08-22T06:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T09:38:31.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b4d7f2dc55a0bd3cb3adf31efa43238ed9291c21","tid":369203,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:54:53.000Z","msg":"牛頭角13歲女童梁婷婷失蹤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170822/photo/bkn-20170822114807184-0822_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170822120926\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170822%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170822114807184-0822_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170822120926&h=a30aeee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n家住牛頭角下邨的13歲女童梁婷婷，於7月1日中午離開住所後便告失蹤，其家人遍尋不獲，於8月16日向警方報案。東九龍總區失蹤人口組接手調查。<br />\n<br />\n梁婷婷身高約1.6米、體重約54公斤、中等身材、圓面型、黃皮膚及蓄長直黑髮。最後露面時身穿深綠色長袖外套、深藍色牛仔褲及黑色運動鞋。任何人士如有該女童的消息或曾見過她，請與警方聯絡。"},{"pid":"e4f4dfaa58dc1aaed4237fa6a5046df34402303f","tid":369203,"uid":14812,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:57:01.000Z","msg":"7月1唔見 8月中先報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db60bcb4ba834887d71e8a7a76a46cc8c19f6d0b","tid":369203,"uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:59:04.000Z","msg":"於7月1日中午離開住所後便告失蹤，其家人遍尋不獲，於8月16日向警方報案"},{"pid":"e3ef35aafa8b47e360e4d3fe751a544b6c9b5f95","tid":369203,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:00:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7月1唔見 8月中先報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n事後清理需時"},{"pid":"1cf8a483a888bf6e9832e798b363c8373847bc28","tid":369203,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:11:15.000Z","msg":"真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個月都唔報警"},{"pid":"6c3570e9de9ef1969b52e15c5fbc154c27bbd257","tid":369203,"uid":117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep